Jun 14, 2021

monday.com Announces Closing of its Initial Public Offering and Full Exercise of Underwriters’ Option to Purchase Additional Shares

NEW YORK & TEL AVIV, Israel - monday.com Ltd. (“monday.com”) today announced the closing of its initial public offering of 3,700,000 ordinary shares at a price of $155.00 per ordinary share. In addition, the underwriters exercised their option to purchase an additional 370,000 ordinary shares at the initial public offering price. The exercise of the underwriters’ option closed concurrently. monday.com’s shares began trading on the Nasdaq Global Select Market on Thursday, June 10, 2021 under the ticker symbol “MNDY.”

---
